cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with motion imitation on humanoids and its application in tele-operation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of RGB-D sensors for motion capture. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with reconstructing motion on humanoids. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also possible categories as the paper presents a framework for finding optimal projections and generating sparse correspondence samples.
